snippet.title: Symphony of War: The Nephilim Saga Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
New Strategy RPG series coming to PC in Summer 2022 - Please add to your Wish List!  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1488200/Symphony_of_War_The_Nephilim_Saga/

I've poured my entire heart and soul into this game for the last 6 years and it's finally about ready to launch - there's so much to it beyond this trailer

Please check out the game website: https://www.dancingdragongames.com/
Join our community discord: https://discord.gg/rmvmGPaKgK
